1. *Daniel* je moj najbolji prijatelj. (*Daniel* is my best friend.)
2. Možda bi *Danielu* trebalo reći istinu. (Maybe we should tell the truth to *Daniel*.)
3. *Danielova* mama je jako ljubazna. (*Daniel's* mom is very kind.)
4. *Daniela* sam sreo u parku sinoć. (I met *Daniela* in the park last night.)
5. *Danielski* jezik se govori u Južnoj Africi. (*Danish* language is spoken in South Africa.)
6. *Danielu* je bilo jako hladno bez jakne. (*Daniel* was very cold without a jacket.)
7. *Danielov* pas je jako sladak. (*Daniel's* dog is very cute.)
8. *Danielska* muzika me opušta. (*Danish* music relaxes me.)
9. *Daniela* i ja smo zajedno učili za ispit. (*Daniela* and I studied together for the exam.)
10. *Danielski* ribolovni alat je jako skup. (*Danish* fishing gear is very expensive.)